00:30.363 --> 00:32.331
I'm out in the prime cut
of the big green.

00:32.432 --> 00:37.062
Behind me is Ed and Rowdy, members
of an up-and-coming subadult gang.

00:37.170 --> 00:40.469
They're challenging everything, including me.
Goes with the territory.

00:40.573 --> 00:44.407
If I show weakness,
if I retreat,

00:44.511 --> 00:46.706
I may be hurt,
I may be killed.

00:46.813 --> 00:50.214
I must hold my own
if I'm gonna stay within this land.

00:50.316 --> 00:52.978
For once there is weakness,
they will exploit it, they will take me out,

00:53.086 --> 00:56.852
they will decapitate me,
they will chop me into bits and pieces.

00:56.956 --> 00:58.924
I'm dead.

00:59.025 --> 01:03.086
But so far, I persevere.

01:03.196 --> 01:04.629
Persevere.

01:06.900 --> 01:09.630
Most times
I'm a kind warrior out here.

01:09.736 --> 01:13.536
Most times, I am gentle,
I am like a flower,

01:13.640 --> 01:17.269
I'm like... I'm like
a fly on the wall,

01:17.377 --> 01:21.473
observing, noncommittal,
noninvasive in any way.

01:21.581 --> 01:24.243
Occasionally I am challenged.
And in that case,

01:24.350 --> 01:27.547
the kind warrior must,
must, must become a samurai.

01:27.654 --> 01:29.679
Must become so,

01:30.757 --> 01:32.782
so formidable,

01:33.993 --> 01:36.461
so fearless of death,

01:36.563 --> 01:37.996
so strong

01:39.132 --> 01:41.794
that he will win, he will win.

01:41.901 --> 01:45.632
Even the bears will believe
that you are more powerful.

01:45.738 --> 01:49.139
And in a sense
you must be more powerful

01:49.242 --> 01:53.372
if you are to survive in this land
with the bear.

01:53.480 --> 01:56.916
No one knew that.
No one ever friggin' knew

01:57.016 --> 02:01.214
that there are times when my life
is on the precipice of death

02:01.321 --> 02:04.552
and that these bears can bite,
they can kill.

02:04.657 --> 02:07.091
And if I am weak,
I go down.

02:07.193 --> 02:09.127
I love them with all my heart.
I will protect them.

02:09.229 --> 02:13.757
I will die for them, but I will not die
at their claws and paws.

02:13.867 --> 02:17.359
I will fight. I will be strong.
I'll be one of them.

02:17.470 --> 02:20.268
I will be... the master.

02:23.076 --> 02:25.374
But still a kind warrior.

02:33.353 --> 02:34.911
Love you, Rowdy.

02:35.021 --> 02:37.512
Give it to me, baby.

02:37.624 --> 02:39.649
That's what I'm talkin' about.
That's what I'm talkin' about.

02:39.759 --> 02:41.624
That's what I'm talkin' about.

02:44.397 --> 02:48.163
I can smell death
all over my fingers.

03:12.091 --> 03:16.858
