What are you doing to that hat?

26:18.176 --> 26:19.905
Where's that hat going?

26:37.996 --> 26:40.191
Hey, who's stealing that hat?

26:40.298 --> 26:43.961
Let me see that hat.
Ghost, I want that hat.

26:45.036 --> 26:47.698
Man! Ghost is bad.

26:49.007 --> 26:51.305
Ghost, what are you doing
